@startuml
title StateSpec Grammar System Member Relationships

skinparam shadowing false
skinparam linetype ortho
skinparam packageStyle rectangle
skinparam classAttributeIconSize 0

class System <<system_decl>> {
  name
}

abstract class SystemMember <<grammar alternative>>

class TenantScope <<system_tenant_scope_decl>> {
  scoped_by
}

class SystemTenant <<system_tenant_decl>> {
  configured
}

class Value <<value_decl>> {
  name
  type
  constraint
}

class Enum <<enum_decl>> {
  name
  members
}

class Shape <<shape_decl>> {
  name
  fields
}

class ExternalSystem <<external_system_decl>> {
  name
  properties
}

class FeatureFlag <<feature_flag_decl>> {
  name
  type
  default
  scope
}

class Log <<log_decl>> {
  name
  level
  event_name
  fields
}

class Metric <<metric_decl>> {
  name
  kind
  unit
  labels
}

class Entity <<entity_decl>> {
  name
  key
  ownership
  fields
}

class StateMachine <<state_machine_decl>> {
  initial
  states
  transitions
}

class Event <<event_decl>> {
  name
  fields
}

class Queue <<queue_decl>> {
  name
  namespace
  channel
}

class Message <<message_decl>> {
  name
  idempotency_key
  payload
}

class Lease <<lease_decl>> {
  name
  resource
  ttl
}

class Worker <<worker_decl>> {
  name
  singleton
  concurrency
}

class ApiServer <<api_server_decl>> {
  name
  serves
  concurrency
}

class Api <<api_decl>> {
  name
  method
  path
  input
  output
  error
}

class Workflow <<workflow_decl>> {
  name
  version
  on
  start
}

class WorkflowStep <<workflow_step_decl>> {
  name
  expected_execution_time
  max_retries
}

class Policy <<policy_decl>> {
  name
  allows
  denies
  quotas
  audits
}

class Annotations <<annotations_block>> {
  entries
}

System *-- SystemMember : system_member*

SystemMember <|-- TenantScope
SystemMember <|-- SystemTenant
SystemMember <|-- Value
SystemMember <|-- Enum
SystemMember <|-- Shape
SystemMember <|-- ExternalSystem
SystemMember <|-- FeatureFlag
SystemMember <|-- Log
SystemMember <|-- Metric
SystemMember <|-- Entity
SystemMember <|-- Event
SystemMember <|-- Queue
SystemMember <|-- Lease
SystemMember <|-- Worker
SystemMember <|-- ApiServer
SystemMember <|-- Api
SystemMember <|-- Workflow
SystemMember <|-- Policy
SystemMember <|-- Annotations

Entity *-- StateMachine : state_machine
Queue *-- Message : messages
Workflow *-- WorkflowStep : steps

Value ..> FeatureFlag : constraint expression
FeatureFlag ..> Entity : optional entity scope
Log ..> Shape : typed fields
Metric ..> Shape : typed labels
Event ..> Shape : typed fields

Entity ..> Entity : relations / children
Entity ..> ExternalSystem : external ownership
Entity ..> Value : field types
Entity ..> Enum : field types
Entity ..> Shape : field types

ApiServer ..> Api : serves
Api ..> Workflow : starts_workflow
Api ..> Queue : enqueues message
Api ..> Shape : input / output / error

Workflow ..> Api : trigger
Workflow ..> Event : trigger / emit
Workflow ..> Message : trigger / enqueue
Workflow ..> Entity : load / mutate
Workflow ..> Lease : acquire / renew / release
Workflow ..> Workflow : start_workflow
Workflow ..> Log : emit
Workflow ..> FeatureFlag : conditional behavior

Worker ..> Queue : polls
Worker ..> Lease : singleton lease
Worker ..> Workflow : executes

Policy ..> Api : allow / deny / audit actions
Policy ..> Workflow : allow / deny / audit actions
Policy ..> Queue : allow / deny / audit actions
Policy ..> FeatureFlag : conditions / quotas

note top of SystemMember
system_member is the grammar union accepted directly
inside system blocks.
end note

note bottom of System
The parser builds AST declarations from these members.
The validator resolves references through the symbol table.
end note

@enduml
